text: (devanuva): imrāngē diyaṇiya vana maryamya. æya tamangē pativata ārakṣā kara gattāya. ebævin ehi (maryam vana æyagē garbhayehi) apagē ātmayangen (ek prāṇayak) pimm̆bemu. æya tama deviyangē āyāvanda dharmayanda satyaya kara tæbū atara (deviyanṭa) sampūrṇayenma avanata vūvangen keneku vaśayenma siṭiyāya
